                  </rs>, the <rs id="t17171016-13-cd78" type="crimeDate">second of this Instant October</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17171016-13-off77 t17171016-13-cd78"></join>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17171016-13-off80 t17171016-13-cd78"></join>. The Prosecutor deposed, the Prisoner came for a pot of Beer, and a quartern of Geneva, leaving a Shilling in his Hand till he brought the pot; and that it growing late, he fell asleep in the Kitchen, having 4 s. in his pocket. The Prosecutor's Wife deposed, that about eleven of the Clock at Night, the Prisoner brought the pot, and came for the Change of his Mony, that there being no Body there but her Husband and she, and her Husband asleep, he would have a pint of Drink, and while she went down to draw the Drink, she supposed he picked her Husband's pocket, for that there had been no Body else there but the Prisoner, and when he was gone, her Husband missed the Mony and Seal; but the Jury not thinking the Evidence sufficient, <rs id="t17171016-13-verdict79" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17171016-13-verdict79" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               acquitted
            </rs> him.</p>
               <p>He was also indicted a second time for <rs id="t17171016-13-off80" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17171016-13-off80" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17171016-13-off80" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing two Rings, value 30 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17171016-13-victim106" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Scot 
                  <interp inst="t17171016-13-victim106" type="surname" value="Scot"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17171016-13-victim106" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17171016-13-victim106" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
